This is Perl module POEIKC.

INSTALLATION

POEIKC installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan POEIKC

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

POEIKC documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc POEIKC

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

SEE ALSO

    % poeikcd --help
    % poikc   --help

    http://arbolbell.jp/poeikcd/   (Japanese site)

Yuji Suzuki
